{"id": 1109, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得职场上的“高情商”有哪些表现？", "description": "你那些棒棒的同事，他们都是怎样的人呢？（题图来自：Hilal Can）", "record_count": 4147, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160710215303bwgAr7aj1KUsikZT.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-08-04T03:00:43Z", "options": [{"id": 104333, "content": "不抱怨 做好自己的每一个任务", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 701184}, {"id": 104455, "content": "不背后嚼舌根，人前亲善懂得换位思考", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 703232}, {"id": 104266, "content": "不甩锅", "image": null, "praise_count": 346, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 582486}, {"id": 104320, "content": "不与同事谈恋爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 107834}, {"id": 104450, "content": "待人和善，說話不帶刺", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 703169}, {"id": 104451, "content": "大智若愚", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1322104}, {"id": 106755, "content": "【能愉快地提高大家的工作效率】", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 712002}, {"id": 104452, "content": "低调完成工作以外的工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698560}, {"id": 107268, "content": "说话滴水不漏", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713855}, {"id": 104456, "content": "做好自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 703245}, {"id": 152841, "content": "不要拆别人快递，不要问能不能拆开来看看，不要评价别人买的零食不好吃，不要把别人买的东西捏来捏去，不要误拆大小重量和自己订单明显不符的快递", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704311}, {"id": 104457, "content": "真诚", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 265401}, {"id": 127243, "content": "做人圆滑，和每个人都相处的和睦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 807482}, {"id": 104460, "content": "永远别让自己或者他人处在尴尬的位置。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 703300}, {"id": 104461, "content": "不甩锅，激情统帅范儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1248782}, {"id": 104462, "content": "做事有分寸", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697063}, {"id": 104463, "content": "清楚自己该做什么，不该做什么，遇事冷静，高效，友善有度。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682838}, {"id": 104464, "content": "老板骂完你，一会儿还要跟你道歉，还得表扬你。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 703316}, {"id": 105488, "content": "别人都觉得你是好人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 607959}, {"id": 104465, "content": "不要不停的显示存在感", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 572822}, {"id": 104466, "content": "不看隔壁同事屏幕", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686426}, {"id": 104467, "content": "对自己负责", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 63495}, {"id": 104468, "content": "朋友们，情商是调控情绪和与人共情的能力，你们是不是对情商有什么误解？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 404003}, {"id": 104470, "content": "不八卦 不抱怨 不传递负能量 表里如一 真诚待人 换位思考", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 703330}, {"id": 104471, "content": "耿直，但能洞悉别人难以觉察的小心思", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682793}, {"id": 104472, "content": "保守别人秘密的同时保守自己的秘密", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670012}, {"id": 104473, "content": "保守别人秘密的同时保守自己的秘密", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670012}, {"id": 104474, "content": "事不关己 高高挂起", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 673792}, {"id": 104475, "content": "沟通效率高，为人谦和，不张扬！对待同事及合作伙伴无论喜欢与否都可以微笑以待！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 703355}, {"id": 104476, "content": "不要有玻璃心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 324761}, {"id": 104477, "content": "乐于助人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672742}, {"id": 104478, "content": "少说多做，不出风头", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 696141}, {"id": 104480, "content": "多听少说。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 432333}, {"id": 104481, "content": "潜规则", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 695827}, {"id": 104482, "content": "别太把自己当回事，也别太把周围人当回事！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 703419}, {"id": 104483, "content": "微笑待人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 703169}, {"id": 104484, "content": "被绝大多数人评价为靠谱", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 677560}, {"id": 112932, "content": "不让别人难堪", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 742539}, {"id": 104485, "content": "呵呵呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 702632}, {"id": 104487, "content": "哈哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692277}, {"id": 105772, "content": "不轻易暴露情绪", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 708147}, {"id": 105519, "content": "管好自己的嘴", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672607}, {"id": 112185, "content": "人生路上，不断学习，坚持运动。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 741587}, {"id": 108351, "content": "平易近人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 422323}, {"id": 177471, "content": "见人下菜碟，碧池碧池碧池", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 965984}, {"id": 106049, "content": "换位思考，学会用高一点的角度思考问题，用低一点的角度待人接物", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 709291}, {"id": 110150, "content": "不会动不动就发起“语音聊天申请”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 729051}, {"id": 104267, "content": "说话声音小…", "image": null, "praise_count": 209, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 603240}, {"id": 104523, "content": "能够影响上司和其他部门和非直属团队成员，促成参与，实现自己的愿景/项目", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 703549}, {"id": 105547, "content": "少说话，多做事，说有智慧的话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 707121}]}